OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,FUnite the Union says the improved
OL,8,Foffer for Birmingham bin workers
OL,9,Fvindicates a year-long struggle.
OL,11,FAfter 16 months of protests, rubbish
OL,12,Fbins piled high and failed agreements,
OL,13,Fa deal was announced today which could
OL,14,Fbring an end to the long-running bin
OL,15,Fstrikes in Birmingham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,FCllr John Cotton, speaking in his role
OL,8,Fas the Labour leader of the council,
OL,9,Fannounced a negotiated settlement was
OL,10,Fnow within sight, which could see
OL,11,Frefuse workers get a one off payment
OL,12,Fof #16,000 - compensation for reduced
OL,13,Fwages.
OL,15,FUnite said the move shows "the power
OL,16,Fof workers" and "how that can be
OL,17,Frealised when they are backed by their
OL,18,Funion".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,FIn a statement, Unite explained why
OL,8,Fthe offer has not been finalised,
OL,9,Fsaying:
OL,11,F"The reason the offer has not yet been
OL,12,Fcompleted and gone to our members is
OL,13,Fbecause at the eleventh hour the
OL,14,Fgovernment backed commissioners
OL,15,Fattempted to stop it, which has led to
OL,16,Ftoday's statement of intent by the
OL,17,Fleader of the council."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,FUnite also says that the full details
OL,8,Fof the deal will remain confidential
OL,9,Fawaiting the detailed offer from the
OL,10,Fcouncil, and it will have to be voted
OL,11,Fon by the bin workers.
OL,13,FThe broad details of the deal have
OL,14,Fbeen released:
OL,16,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,17,Fsaid:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"As I have said on many occasions, the
OL,8,Fworkers come first and we will always
OL,9,Fdo everything in our power to ensure
OL,10,Fthat our members are treated with
OL,11,Fdignity and respect.
OL,13,F"The move made today by the leader of
OL,14,Fthe council is a vindication of the
OL,15,Fbin workers' struggle for a decent
OL,16,Fdeal.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"Over the last few months, there have
OL,8,Fbeen intense negotiations to get the
OL,9,Fblocked "ballpark" deal back on the
OL,10,Ftable, so that our members could vote
OL,11,Fon it.
OL,13,F"The reason why we are not yet at that
OL,14,Fstage is purely down to the vindictive
OL,15,Finterference of the government backed
OL,16,Fcommissioners who have attempted to
OL,17,Fblock the deal again and clearly
OL,18,Foverstepped their remit.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IOUqD@RO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"Their lack of both experience and
OL,8,Findustrial relations competence has
OL,9,Fbeen a major factor in this dispute,
OL,10,Fand their malevolent game playing has
OL,11,Fbeen an absolute disgrace.
OL,13,F"The commissioner model is a licence
OL,14,Ffor a few unelected individuals to
OL,15,Fprint money and play games.
OL,17,F"They have let the workers down, the
OL,18,Fpeople of Birmingham down and the
OL,19,Fcouncil down.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"I salute the fortitude of my members
OL,8,Fwho have needlessly been forced to
OL,9,Fendure months of attacks and hardship
OL,10,Fto get us to this point.
OL,12,F"I thank mayor Richard Parker and Lord
OL,13,FBrendan Barber for the important roles
OL,14,Fboth have played in getting us to this
OL,15,Fpoint.
OL,17,F"And I thank the people of Birmingham
OL,18,Ffor their continued patience and
OL,19,Fsupport."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,FOnay Kasab, National Lead Officer for
OL,8,FUnite the Union said the deal on the
OL,9,Ftable includes a compensation package
OL,10,Fof #16,000.
OL,12,FCllr John Cotton said it's been a
OL,13,Fdifficult process to get to this point:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"This has been a challenging and
OL,8,Fcomplex process, but after months of
OL,9,Fhard work, on the principles and
OL,10,Fparameters of a deal, I believe a new
OL,11,Fimproved offer can be made and terms
OL,12,Fcan be put in place that address the
OL,13,F"ballpark issues" discussed at ACAS
OL,14,Fthat Unite members can agree in order
OL,15,Fto end the strike once and for all.
OL,17,F"A deal that would be good for the
OL,18,Fworkforce, represent good value for
OL,19,Fmoney and would not repeat the
OL,20,Fmistakes of the past and risk creating
OL,21,Fnew structural equal pay liabilities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"I want our workforce to be able to
OL,8,Freturn to work and help us deliver the
OL,9,Fquality refuse and recycling services
OL,10,Fthe people of this city deserve.
OL,12,F"That's why throughout this dispute I
OL,13,Fhave resisted those who would dismiss
OL,14,Fthe striking workers instead of
OL,15,Fnegotiating.
OL,17,F"I have instructed officers to move
OL,18,Fforward with negotiations so that we
OL,19,Fcan bring this matter to a close.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"Whilst the pre-election period
OL,8,Fprevents the Council from making a
OL,9,Ffinal decision prior to 7 May, a re-
OL,10,Felected Labour administration under my
OL,11,Fleadership will work to get this deal
OL,12,Fapproved as a matter of absolute
OL,13,Fpriority.
OL,15,F"The council can then move forward and
OL,16,Foffer the people of Birmingham the
OL,17,Fservices that they deserve.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777460573
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike: Union says
OL,4,Cimproved offer 'vindicates' year-long
OL,5,Cstruggle
OL,7,F"I also want to re-emphasise my
OL,8,Fabsolute determination to see through
OL,9,Fthe agreement reached with the
OL,10,Fcouncil's unions last year that will
OL,11,Fdeliver the pay justice that thousands
OL,12,Fof women workers were denied under
OL,13,Fprevious leaderships.
OL,15,F"I would like to thank the people of
OL,16,FBirmingham for their patience during
OL,17,Fthis challenging time".
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
